      <link>https://github.com/Argent77/NearInfinity/releases/tag/v1.36-20151216</link>
    </file>
    <changelog>
      <entry>Major overhaul of the datatypes used in structured resources.</entry>
      <entry>Added new Tools->Check->For Illegal Strrefs... feature.</entry>
      <entry>Added "Expiry time" field to Item structures in ARE resources.</entry>
      <entry>BS scripts can be selected in relevant resource reference fields.</entry>
      <entry>Extended parameter 2 of opcode 58 (Dispel Effects) in Enhanced Editions.</entry>
      <entry>Updated params of opcode 294 (Set Existence Delay).</entry>
      <entry>Improved descriptions of value fields in GAM's Variable structures.</entry>
      <entry>Fixed infinite blocking bug when opening games via bookmarks.</entry>
      <entry>Fixed a bug which occasionally caused errors in various search routines.</entry>
      <entry>Fixed a bug in "Secondary projectile" field of PRO resources.</entry>
      <entry>Fixed Master/Current area field labels in GAM resources.</entry>
      <entry>Fixed Kit field type in IWD2.</entry>
      <entry>Several more bugfixes and improvements.</entry>
    </changelog>
  </release>

